>>Another tangent: Phil Knight, the head honcho
at Nike, is often credited with taking "branding"
to incredible economic returns. ...Other
corporations, and VW obviously, are following
suit...By grabbing as many VW-related
words/logos/whatever, the ad or product dept. at
